
# 5. Add Logger module

Date: 2022-02-10

## Status

Accepted

## Context

The idea is to modularize the source code of Planetary in different modules to keep the code more organized and prevent dependencies from permeate different parts of the code.

## Decision

The following guide was followed: https://developer.apple.com/documentation/swift_packages/organizing_your_code_with_local_packages. Swift packages will be used to create modules.

## Consequences

- No impact in performance is expected.
